# Services Directory

This directory contains Angular services for API communication and business logic.

## Planned Services

- `technician.service.ts` - Technician API service
- `job.service.ts` - Job API service
- `scheduling.service.ts` - Scheduling and assignment service
- `time-tracking.service.ts` - Time tracking service
- `reporting.service.ts` - Reporting service
- `frm-signalr.service.ts` - SignalR real-time updates service
- `notification.service.ts` - Notification service
- `geolocation.service.ts` - Geolocation service
- `export.service.ts` - Data export service
